{#-
  Callout component: small mono eyebrow label + one Hanken body sentence.

  Expects a single `callout` variable in scope:
    callout: {label: str, body: str}

  Stack callouts vertically by including this partial inside a for-loop in
  the parent template (see poster_scoreboard.html.j2). No card container,
  no rounded corners, no shadow. Hairline rule is owned by the caller.
-#}
<div class="callout">
  <div class="callout-label eyebrow">{{ callout.label }}</div>
  <div class="callout-body">{{ callout.body }}</div>
</div>
